public void mineBlock(int prefix, ArrayList<Block> blockchain) {
    String prefixString = "0".repeat(prefix);
    if (hash == null) hash = calculateBlockHash();

    while (!hash.startsWith(prefixString)) {
        nonce++;
        hash = calculateBlockHash();
    }
    System.out.print("Block mined! Nonce = " + nonce + " Hash = " + hash);
}

Implements block mining through nonce and SHA-256 hash-prefix 


public String calculateBlockHash() {
    String dataToHash = previousHash + Long.toString(timestamp) + Integer.toString(nonce) + data.toString();
    MessageDigest digest = MessageDigest.getInstance("SHA-256");
    byte[] bytes = digest.digest(dataToHash.getBytes(StandardCharsets.UTF_8));
    StringBuilder buffer = new StringBuilder();
    for (byte b : bytes) {
        buffer.append(String.format("%02x", b));
    }
    return buffer.toString();
}

Calculates a unique has for each block to maintain integrity


